dct_description_sm: State road map. Relief shown by shading and spot heights. "95-4." "AAA topography adapted from NASA Landsat satellite imagery." "This map published annually." Insets: Niagara Falls area -- Rochester -- Utica -- Albany -- Buffalo -- Syracuse. Includes text and color illustrations. Notes, indexes, "Toll facilities" directory, "Southern New York State area map", Long Island road map, "Driving distances" inset and Long Island inset on verso. "5137 F."
